<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thank You for Your Order!</h1>
    <p>Dear Customer,</p>
    <p>Your order has been placed.Thank you for your purchase. Below are your order details:</p>
    <hr>

    <p><strong>Products:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <% @order.order_items.each do |item| %>
        <li>
          <%= item.product.name %> (Quantity: <%= item.quantity %>)
        </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Status:</strong> <%= @order.status.capitalize %></p>
    <p><strong>Shipping Address:</strong> <%= @order.user.shipping_detail.address %></p>
    <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
    <p>You can view your order details by clicking the link below:</p>
    <p><a href="<%= order_url(@order) %>">View Your Order</a></p>
    <hr>
    <p>&copy; <%= Date.today.year %> UnderCut Surgical Industries. All rights reserved.</p>
  </body>
</html>
